:"critical","suggested_fix":"Either (a) verify the 're-home story' dependency creates docs/ticket-model.md before this story executes, or (b) replace 'ticket-model→docs/ticket-model.md' with a pointer to an existing doc (docs/user-guide.md covers ticket lifecycle and types in detail).","tier":"LLM","validity":0.7778,"verification":{"binary":{"absence_confirmed_in_context":"yes","cited_reference_accurate":"yes","claims_absence":"yes","committed_work_relies_on_unbacked_claim":"yes","evidence_entails_finding":"yes","impact_follows_necessarily":"yes","is_verifiable":"yes","no_existing_mitigation":"no","no_viable_alternative_explanation":"no","path_reachable":"yes","respects_artifact_altitude":"yes","severity_claim_justified":"yes"},"severity_attributes":{"ac_unverifiable":"none","blast_radius":"local","debt_impact":"low","divergent_implementation":"low","dod_uncertifiable":"none","internal_conflict":"none","irreversible_without_rationale":"none","likelihood":"high","prod_impact":"low","reversibility":"easy","silent_vs_self_revealing":"self_revealing","undecomposed":"none","vague_directive":"none"}}},{"block_threshold":0.7,"blocking_enabled":true,"checklist_item":"- [ ] Resolve the missing `docs/ticket-model.md` pointer target: either confirm it will be created by a dependency story before this one merges (and make that a hard `Depends on:` in Scope), substitute an existing doc (e.g. `docs/user-guide.md`), or remove the pointer and inline only the essential rule.","cohort":["T8"],"criteria":["T8"],"decision":"advisory","drop_reason":null,"evidence":["Plan text: 'POINTER: ticket-model→docs/ticket-model.md'","docs/ directory listing: no ticket-model.md file present","search_files for 'docs/ticket-model.md' returns only cache hits from other plan-review findings flagging the same absence","No fallback specified (e.g. 'use docs/user-guide.md if ticket-model.md does not exist')"],"finding":"The De-risking POINTER list references 'ticket-model→docs/ticket-model.md' as a pointe